column1: query
SELECT i.original_artist, i.name, i.language FROM songs AS i WHERE i.id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  i.id <= 28 GROUP BY i.language HAVING COUNT(i.language) > 0 LIMIT 7;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T3.language), T1.name, T3.original_artist FROM participants T1 INNER JOIN performance_score T2 ON T1.id = T2.participant_id INNER JOIN songs T3 ON T2.songs_id = T3.id WHERE T2.stage_presence BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T2.participant_id < 18 GROUP BY T3.original_artist ORDER BY T3.original_artist DESC;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T2.popularity), T1.english_translation FROM songs AS T1 JOIN performance_score AS T3 ON T3.songs_id = T1.id JOIN participants AS T2 ON T2.id = T3.participant_id WHERE T3.stage_presence BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY T1.english_translation ORDER BY T1.english_translation DESC LIMIT 6;
SELECT rhythm_tempo FROM performance_score JOIN participants ON participants.id = performance_score.participant_id WHERE participant_id < 29 LIMIT 5
SELECT AVG(voice_sound_quality), voice_sound_quality, songs_id FROM performance_score GROUP BY songs_id, voice_sound_quality HAVING SUM(participant_id) = 60 ORDER BY AVG(voice_sound_quality) LIMIT 8;

SELECT COUNT(songs_id), voice_sound_quality FROM performance_score JOIN participants ON participants.id = performance_score.participant_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM performance_score AS e WHERE e.voice_sound_quality BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  e.participant_id < 35 AND participants.id = e.participant_id LIMIT 1) GROUP BY voice_sound_quality
SELECT language FROM performance_score JOIN songs ON performance_score.songs_id = songs.id WHERE rhythm_tempo = 37 ORDER BY participant_id, songs_id, language ASC LIMIT 1
SELECT u.popularity, u.name FROM participants AS u WHERE u.popularity BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY u.name ASC
SELECT id, name, popularity FROM participants GROUP BY popularity HAVING MIN(id) >= 77

SELECT COUNT(stage_presence), COUNT(DISTINCT stage_presence), id FROM performance_score JOIN participants ON participants.id = performance_score.participant_id WHERE participants.popularity = 90 LIMIT 5
SELECT name FROM participants WHERE id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND popularity NOT IN (SELECT popularity FROM participants AS w WHERE w.popularity BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  w.popularity = 41 LIMIT 8)
SELECT b.id FROM songs AS b LIMIT 7
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT z.id) FROM participants AS z WHERE z.popularity BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND name NOT IN (SELECT name FROM songs AS l)
SELECT songs_id, rhythm_tempo FROM performance_score LIMIT 9
SELECT COUNT(participant_id), MAX(participant_id), COUNT(DISTINCT participant_id) FROM performance_score WHERE stage_presence = 60;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p.name), ps.stage_presence, s.original_artist FROM participants p JOIN performance_score ps JOIN songs s ON p.id = ps.participant_id AND ps.songs_id = s.id
SELECT english_translation FROM songs WHERE id = 61 OR id < (SELECT MIN(id) FROM songs AS s LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT voice_sound_quality), participant_id, songs_id, rhythm_tempo FROM performance_score WHERE songs_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR songs_id > 20 GROUP BY participant_id, songs_id, rhythm_tempo

SELECT COUNT(id), COUNT(DISTINCT language), english_translation, language FROM songs WHERE id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR id IN (SELECT id FROM participants AS j WHERE  j.id <= 46) GROUP BY language HAVING MAX(id) = 49
SELECT name FROM participants WHERE popularity < 75 OR popularity = (SELECT MAX(popularity) FROM participants ORDER BY popularity DESC LIMIT 1)
SELECT MIN(voice_sound_quality), COUNT(rhythm_tempo) FROM performance_score JOIN songs ON performance_score.songs_id = songs.id WHERE  participant_id > 19 LIMIT 7
SELECT AVG(participant_id) FROM participants JOIN performance_score ON performance_score.participant_id = participants.id JOIN songs ON performance_score.songs_id = songs.id WHERE  rhythm_tempo = 97;
SELECT s.id, s.original_artist, s.english_translation FROM participants p JOIN performance_score ps ON p.id = ps.participant_id JOIN songs s ON ps.songs_id = s.id WHERE p.id != 70

SELECT T1.english_translation, T2.songs_id, T2.rhythm_tempo FROM songs AS T1 JOIN performance_score AS T2 ON T1.id = T2.songs_id WHERE T2.voice_sound_quality >= 37 AND T2.songs_id NOT IN (SELECT songs_id FROM performance_score WHERE stage_presence = 44 LIMIT 6) GROUP BY T1.english_translation, T2.songs_id, T2.rhythm_tempo HAVING SUM(T2.rhythm_tempo) <= 25 ORDER BY T1.english_translation DESC LIMIT 1
